rows.label: tlk000014_msg0001
rows.name:
You're heading to Temperantia?
Well, just give the word and we can
prepare a Divine Beast ship for you...

rows.label: tlk000014_msg0005
rows.name: Then let's set sail at once.

rows.label: tlk000014_msg0006
rows.name:
We don't know what the situation on
Temperantia is like. Just make sure
you're fully prepared.
